descriptionModels.description: As a nocturnal race, you have superior vision in dim conditions. You can see in dim light within 60 feet of you as if it were bright light

Because of your claws, you have a climbing speed of 20 ft. Additionally, your claws are natural weapons, which you can use to make unarmed strikes. The damage die for your unarmed strike is a d4, and it deals slashing damage instead of bludgeoning damage
You may add half your proficiency bonus, rounded down, to your initiative rolls
You can communicate simple ideas with feline creatures, such as cats, lions, and tigers
